öling, M., Modell, M., Peters, W.A., Tester, J., Environmental assessment of supercritical water oxidation of sewage sludge (2004) Resources, Conservation and Recycling, 41, pp. 321-338; Tester, J.W., Holgate, H.R., Armellini, F.J., Webley, P.A., Kililea, W.R., Hong, G.T., Barner, H.E., (1993) Supercritical Water Oxidation Technology, Process Development and Fundamental Research, 518, pp. 35-76. , American Chemical Society Symposium Series; (2003) The Network for Transports and the Environment, , http://www.ntm.a.se; Regulations for certified environmental product declarations, EPD (2000) Svensk Tillämpning Av ISO TR 14025 TYP III Miljödeklarationer (Swedish Application of ISO TR 14025 Type III Environmental Declarations), , http://www.miljostyrning.se/; Tillman, A.-M., Svingby, M., Lundström, H., Life cycle assessment of municipal waste water systems (1998) International Journal of Life Cycle Assessment, 3, pp. 145-157","Svanström, M.; Chemical Engineering and Environmental Science, Chalmers University of Technology, SE-412 96 Göteborg, Sweden; email: magdalena.svanstrom@chemeng.chalmers.se",,,,,,,,0734242X,,WMARD,,"English","Waste Manage. Res.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-33749437714
